<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Based on what you told us, you can apply for <%= claim.has_ecp_policy? ? "an" : "a" %> <%= policy_name(claim) %> of:</h2>

<p class="govuk-heading-l"><%= number_to_currency(claim.award_amount, precision: 0) %></p>

<%= button_to "Apply now", claim_path(current_policy_routing_name), method: :patch, class: "govuk-button", role: :button, data: { module: "govuk-button"}, params: { claim: { eligibility_attributes: { award_amount: current_claim.award_amount } } } %>


<h2 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-top-6">About your additional payment</h2>

<%= render partial: "eligibility_guidance_#{claim.policy.locale_key}" %>

<p class="govuk-body">
  So long as your circumstances stay the same, you may be able to claim for additional payments next year. This may depend on the years you studied or when you began teaching.
</p>
